        <body>
            <pb n="1"/>
            <p rend="align(center)">
                <placeName>New York</placeName>
                <date>Sept. 15th 1864</date>
            </p>
            <p>
                <addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>
            </p>
            <p>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
            </p>
            <pb n="2"/>
            <p>
                <add>Hebrew</add>
            </p>
            <p>
                <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
                <del>94 East</del>
            </p>
            <p>
                <placeName>94 East Broadway</placeName>
            </p>
            <pb n="3"/>
            <p rend="align(right)"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>September 15,
                1864</date>.</p>
            <p><addressee>Reverend Isaac Leeser</addressee>,
                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>,</p>
            <p>Honored Sir:</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Please send me, in gilt, a set of Portuguese holiday<lb/> prayer
                books as well as a prayer book and one for the four fasts.<lb/> If you should have
                none of the small edition, nicely bound, you<lb/> may send me a set of the large
                edition. Should you have none of<lb/> the handsomely bound ones, you may send me a
                set in calfskin.<lb/> Write to me of the bill without <sic>comissions</sic> for
                discount, but put<lb/> the discount to my credit. If possible, send the holiday
                prayer<lb/> books tomorrow, if not, next <date>Monday</date>.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">I shall pay the bill immediately upon the receipt<lb/> of it. The
                buyer of these books departs from here on <date>Tuesday</date>.<lb/> Therefore these
                holiday prayer books must be sent out <date>Monday</date> at<lb/> the latest.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">Signed, Devotedly,</p>
            <p rend="indent(10)">
                <persName role="author">Michael Light</persName>
            </p>
            <p rend="indent(11)">
                <placeName>94 East Broadway</placeName>
            </p>
        </body>
